      </a>
      :
      <b>
       th tr cst f stff
      </b>
     </h2>
     <div class="entry">
      <p>
       Oftn w thnk bt cttng dwn n wht w by bcs w’d lk t b frgl, nd sv mny. And I’m ll fr tht.
      </p>
      <p>
       Bt thr’s mr t byng lss. Wy mr.
      </p>
      <p>
       Th cst f prchsng n tm jst scrtchs th srfc. Whn w by smthng, w r tkng t nt r hms, r lvs, nd w r tkng n th lf f nthr bjct n ths wrld.
      </p>
      <p>
       Th lf f n bjct? Bt srly y’v gn md, L.
      </p>
      <p>
       It’s ntrly pssbl I hv — I’m tlkng t myslf n ths pst, ftr ll. Bt hr m t, O hypthtcl rdr n my mnd.
      </p>
      <p>
       An bjct sn’t brn n th str. It s brn n th wds (f t s wd), n th mns (f t’s mtl), n th dpths f th wrld (n th cs f ptrlm-bsd prdcts sch s plstcs, synthtc txtls nd sch), r prhps ll thr plcs nd mr f t’s  cmbntn f mtrls. It’s brn whn ths ntrl rsrcs r mnd r hrvstd (t grt cst nd grt cst t th nvrnmnt), nd thn hld t  fctry smwhr,  fctry tht pllts, nvtbly. It’s shpd nd shftd nt ts fnl frm (ftn n vrs fctrs), thn shppd t vrs dstrbtn systms nd fnlly t th rtlr.
       <span id="more-390">
       </span>
      </p>
      <p>
       I sy fnlly, bt t’s fr frm fnl. Th lf f ths bjct hs jst bgn t ntr r lvs, vn thgh w’v lrdy pd fr th dstrctn f r Erth jst t wn t.
      </p>
      <p>
       Nw w mst trnsprt t hm, frthr plltng nd cnsmng nd pyng — pyng fr th cst f fl nd mntnnc f r trnsprttn, nlss t’s hmn-pwrd, s wll s th cst f tm, prcs scnds f r lvs tht w’ll nvr gt bck).
      </p>
      <p>
       All f tht spnt, t nw ccps vlbl rl stt n r hms (r ffcs), rl stt tht cld g t lvng spc, r rl stt tht w cld gv p f w hd lss stff nd  smllr hm. Ths s rl stt tht’s rlly xpnsv, btw: w py xrbtnt prcs t wn r rnt  hm, nd vry sqr ft f tht hm csts s mr prcs tm tht w spnd wrkng t rn th mny t py fr tht rl stt. And tht’s jst fr rnt r mrtgg. Add n th cst f pwr r gs t ht r cl tht hm, th cst f mntnng th hm, nd th tm w spnd mntnng nd clnng nd dclttrng nd rgnzng tht hm nd th stff n t.
      </p>
      <p>
       And yt, w’v stll nly scrtchd th srfc. Th tm, f t’s lctrnc, rqrs pwr. All th tm. Th tm nds t b mntnd. Swtchd n nd ff, clnd, ld, nd ctn tkn nt t brk t. Ths r mr prcs scnds, prcs dllrs. If t’s wd r mtl r glss, t mght nd t b plshd. It mght brk  bt nd nd rprng. W hv t str ts wrrnty smwhr, nd nt frgt bt tht (mr mntl cycls spnt). W mght hv spcl tls fr t, clnng prdcts, ccssrs. All f ths rqr spc nd cr nd mny.
      </p>
      <p>
       And yt, w’r nt vn hlfwy thr. I’ll spr y th rst f th nrrtv nd jst mk  lst.
      </p>
      <p>
       And ths s nly  prtl lst. Sm csts f wnng stff:
      </p>
      <ul>
       <li>
        It clttrs r spc, csng dstrctns nd strss.
       </li>
       <li>
        W mst cnstntly mv t t gt t thr stff, t cln, t rgnz, t pnt wlls r dcrt r rmdl.
       </li>
       <li>
        W mst tk t wth s f w mv, nd ftn f w trvl. Tht’s  tn f trbl nd csts.
       </li>
       <li>
        Oftn w py fr xtr strg, tsd n r yrds r n strg fclts.
       </li>
       <li>
        If t brks, w wll ftn tk t t b rprd.
       </li>
       <li>
        If w hv kds r pts, w hv t wrry bt t gttng brkn, r scld thm fr nt bng crfl wth t.
       </li>
       <li>
        If w gt sd t t, nd t brks, w’ll rplc t bcs w thnk w nd t.
       </li>
       <li>
        If t gts ld nd crtchty, w hv th hdch f pttng p wth  lss-thn-fnctnng tl.
       </li>
       <li>
        If w hv t mch stff, t wghs s dwn, mtnlly.
       </li>
       <li>
        W gt ttchd t r stff, crtng n mtnl bttl whn w cnsdr gvng t p (whthr w ctlly gv t p r nt).
       </li>
       <li>
        If w hv t mch stff, w lv n  crmpd spc, nd dn’t hv rm fr r thr stff.
       </li>
       <li>
        T mch stff css mr msss nd s hrdr t cln.
       </li>
       <li>
        W mght trp vr stff nd hrt rslvs.
       </li>
       <li>
        If w dn’t trp vr t, w mst wrry bt tht ch tm w pss by th tm.
       </li>
       <li>
        If w wnt nt dbt byng th stff, w mst dl wth ll th pn nd wrry f tht dbt, ddd t thr dbt.
       </li>
       <li>
        Evn f w dn’t g nt dbt, thr’s th ddd brdn f dlng wth th fnncl trnsctn n r chckng rgstrs r fnncl sftwr, r rcnclng t wth th bnk sttmnt. If w vn bthr, bcs smtms t’s jst t mch.
       </li>
       <li>
        It gvs s  fls sns f scrty.
       </li>
       <li>
        It rdcs th tm w hv t spnd dng thngs, nstd f wrryng bt, clnng, mntnng, sng, nd wrkng t py fr stff.
       </li>
       <li>
        It rdcs th qlty f th tm w d hv.
       </li>
       <li>
        At sm pnt, w mst wrry bt (nd spnd tm nd mny n) gttng rd f th tm. Ths mns tm nd mny spnt n Eby, Crglst,  yrdsl, gvng t t  chrty r frnd r rltv (nd th drvng rqrd t d tht), tkng t  clssfd d, dlng wth byrs, nd s n. A rl hdch.
       </li>
       <li>
        If y d nd lv yr stff, yr rltvs wll hv t dl wth ll f t. A rl hdch ndd.
       </li>
       <li>
        If, gdnss frbd,  ntrl dsstr hppns, r yr hm gts brgld, y’ll hv t dl wth th mtnl lss f stff.
       </li>
      </ul>
      <p>
       I cld g n, s y cn prbbly tll. Thr s n wy t clclt th tr cst f stff, s t’s wy t cmplctd t pt nmbrs n.
      </p>
      <p>
       Jst rmmbr ll f tht, whn y cnsdr gttng n tm — vn f t’s sppsdly fr. Nthng s fr, whn y cnsdr ll f th bv. Ar y rdy t dl wth th lf f tht tm, nd th lf y’r gng t gv p t wn t?
      </p>
